    "title": "Technical Data Advisory Service",
    "excerpt": "<p>Learn more about our technical advisory service. Overview We recognize other capable fellow colleagues at the state may want to build a data stack or use advanced analysis tools, but lack a thought-partner to discuss and refine ideas. We aim to provide these colleagues with advice about how to define, scope, and build a robust &#8230; <a title=\"Technical Data Advisory Service\" class=\"read-more\" href=\"https://live-digital-ca-gov.pantheonsite.io/work-with-us/technical-data-advisory-service/\" aria-label=\"More on Technical Data Advisory Service\">Read more</a></p>\n",
